dataStudio.name: SimilarWeb Visits & Engagement
dataStudio.description: SimilarWeb lets you measure the Digital World. View the number of monthly Visits, Unique Visitors, Bounce Rate, Pages per Visit and Average Visit Duration for up to 25 domains. You will need a SimilarWeb API key to use this connector; please visit https://www.similarweb.com if you don't have a SimilarWeb PRO account.
